Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 朱雷一天量四次体温，除了吃饭，都要戴好口罩。
Peng Pai journalist Julie took his temperature four times a day, wearing a mask in addition to eating.
这已经成为李奥（化名）复工以来的日常。
This has become a daily routine for Leo (alias) since he returned to work.
他在广东省潮州市一家电子元件公司做设备管理，自从12日解除隔离，他到目前已经复工6天了。
He works as an equipment manager at an electronics component company in Chaozhou, Guangdong Province, and has been back to work for six days since he was unquarantined on the 12th.
2月18日，李奥告诉澎湃新闻，公司改变了食堂的格局。
On Feb. 18, Li told Pong Pai News that the company had changed the structure of the canteen.
“为了避免员工面对面就餐，公司特意把食堂里两边落座的凳子拆了一边，这样大家只能朝一个方向落座。
"To avoid a face-to-face meal, the company purposely took the chairs off the sides of the cafeteria so that everyone could only sit in one direction.
”水龙头和洗手液也都改成了感应式的。
The faucet and hand sanitizer have also been made inductive.
公司食堂只能朝同一方向落座。
The company canteen can only sit in the same direction.
来源：均为受访者提供“每天坐班车去公司，车上都能闻到消毒水的味道。
www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cn "Take a bus to the company every day.
”李奥说。
'said Leo.
上车之前，司机都会给每位乘客量体温，进公司大门之前还要再量一次。
Before getting on the bus, the driver takes the temperature of each passenger and measures it again before entering the company gate.
上下午上班期间，主管负责人再次登记所有员工的体温。
During the morning and afternoon work, the supervisor re-registers the temperature of all the staff.
人手少，是李奥复工以来最深刻的感受，过去他只负责设备管理，而现在他却要“一个人当成三个人用”，除了本职工作，他还要操作机器以及负责产品故障排查。
The lack of staff was one of Li's deepest feelings since resuming work. He used to be in charge of equipment management, but now he wants to be "one man for three." In addition to his job, he also operates machines and troubleshoots products.
“我们项目组同时招来的五名同事，目前就到了我一个。
"I have five colleagues on our project team who are now on my team.
”上周末，他正常上班。
He went to work normally last weekend.
“现在很害怕机器坏掉，因为一坏就涉及到各种人找我，我实在脱不开身。
"I'm afraid the machine will break down, because it involves all kinds of people looking for me and I can't get away from it.
”李奥向澎湃新闻表示，目前公司生产产量没达到要求，不过没差太多，还在赶进度。
Li told Peng Pai News that production at the moment was not up to par, but not too far from it, and was on track.
他说，他们主要是网上办公。
'They work mainly online, 'he says.
遇到问题，他经常通过电话联系没来公司的同事帮忙解决。
When confronted with a problem, he often calls his co-worker to help solve the problem.
李奥表示，因为新冠肺炎疫情，公司原本通知正月初七上班的时间被推迟，目前公司仍未宣布正式的上班时间，“但只要隔离时间到了，就可以来上班，看个人情况。
Li said that because of the outbreak of pneumonia in the first month of the company's notification to work was postponed, the company has not announced the official business hours, "but as long as the isolation time, can come to work, to see personal circumstances.
”湖北的同事如果实在来不了，也没硬性要求。
Hubei's colleagues have no hard and fast requirements if they really can't come.
水龙头改成了感应式对赶回潮州准备复工的员工，公司把原本的三人套间提供给需要隔离的员工一个人住。
The faucet was changed to inductive pairs of employees returning to Chaozhou to get back to work, and the company offered the original three-person suite to an isolated employee.
每天都有人送盒饭，还准备了方便面、面包、牛奶等食品供隔离期的员工选择。
Boxed meals are delivered every day, and foods such as instant noodles, bread and milk are prepared for employees to choose from during the quarantine period.
李奥隔离期结束后，回到了自己原来住的宿舍，公司派发了消毒用品。
After Li's isolation period ended, he returned to his former dormitory, and the company distributed disinfectant supplies.
米面粮油等，由专人在附近的超市买好送到门口。
Rice flour oil and so on, by hand in the nearby supermarket to buy good delivery to the door.
